{"tid":1773292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"點名劉亦菲、李連杰、吳亦凡 內地網警：不准有雙重國籍","createTime":"2019-12-07T10:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T11:22:32.000Z","uid":41343,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"913a4567d907c1591b62583426f095c18056f68f","tid":1773292,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:56:00.000Z","msg":"內地不允許公民擁有雙重國籍，但不少藝人「側側膊」，取得外國國籍後還在使用中國護照，黑龍江鶴崗市網警今日在短片平台上載一條「教育」短片，以劉亦菲、吳亦凡及李連杰做例子，強調「中國不承認雙國籍，放棄(中國籍)即禁止使用中國護照。對於違反規定沒註銷護照的，大使館將註銷他們的證件，嚴重者拒絕入境」，呼籲「堅持一人一國籍」，又指「不強制或違背本人意願選擇國籍」。<br />\n<br />\n有內地網媒隨即「起底」，指劉亦菲是湖北武漢人，後來隨母親去美國並取得美國國籍；吳亦凡出生於廣東廣州，10歲隨母親移民加拿大溫哥華，取得加拿大國籍。李連杰則是北京人，2009年，有外媒指他已入籍新加坡並在當地置產。<br />\n<br />\n報道直言，隨著國家發展，目前已經加強管控雙重國籍的外籍華人，凡不註銷中國護照的外籍華人，都無法進入中國，「網友對此也是十分支持，相信李連杰、劉亦菲、吳亦凡等擁有海外國籍的華人明星一定會給大家做出好的表率」。"},{"pid":"9657019d3e80ae607fe17c604a4999216d2fd9cf","tid":1773292,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:59:18.000Z","msg":"大灣區要鎖國了準備"},{"pid":"90c61709009886575a648fc2827f705ae67a2180","tid":1773292,"uid":267471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"GG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c506819835c30c3f01aa8457785af76f5cc7bfa","tid":1773292,"uid":175590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T11:04:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3345332c92eee3c56e4969f67a1c1d49354f95ea","tid":1773292,"uid":28223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T11:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擁有雙重國籍的都是間諜 都是漢奸"},{"pid":"7e4e49f5dfe9898a50041671c7606208c5205004","tid":1773292,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T11:15:26.000Z","msg":"又話唔比李生做中國人<br />\n咁易原諒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f9a1171059497c37fc0ffe9fccba4ae091299c","tid":1773292,"uid":76935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T11:22:32.000Z","msg":"維尼全家好似都有加拿大綠卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}